OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1777543610
OL,3,CTribunal strikes off solicitor at
OL,4,CCumbrian law firm Cartmell Shepherd
OL,6,FA solicitor at the Cumbrian law firm
OL,7,FCartmell Shepherd has been struck off
OL,8,Fafter admitting to payment
OL,9,Firregularities of around #216,000.
OL,11,FA tribunal heard that Nicholas Devlin,
OL,12,F39, had moved the money from client
OL,13,Faccounts to pay for bills that had
OL,14,Fnever been sent.
OL,16,FHe was also found to have tried to
OL,17,Fstop people from finding out about the
OL,18,Firregularities by asking other staff
OL,19,Fmembers not to send out bills to
OL,20,Fclients, in case they requested
OL,21,Fprogress updates on cases.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
